T</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/cosmic-collision-of-galaxies-mapped-by-maunakea-telescope</guid></item><item><title>索马鲁肽通过不依赖体重减轻的代谢恢复机制改善骨关节炎进展</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/semaglutide-ameliorates-osteoarthritis-progression-through-a-weight-loss-independent-metabolic-restoration-mechanism</link><description>通过索马鲁肽改善骨关节炎的独立于减肥的机制。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/semaglutide-ameliorates-osteoarthritis-progression-through-a-weight-loss-independent-metabolic-restoration-mechanism.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 12:01:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/semaglutide-ameliorates-osteoarthritis-progression-through-a-weight-loss-independent-metabolic-restoration-mechanism</guid></item><item><title>推进患者可在护理场所使用的细胞和基因疗法的制造</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/advancing-the-manufacture-of-patient-accessible-cell-and-gene-therapies-at-place-of-care</link><description>一家医学院、一家非营利组织和一家生物技术公司组成的合作伙伴关系，旨在开发和制造一种可访问且商业上可行的造血干细胞 (HSC) 制造平台，用于治疗镰状细胞病 (SCD) 等疾病。该联盟结合了 Trenchant BioSystems 自动化患者特异性细胞和基因治疗 (CGT) 流程的技术、马萨诸塞大学陈医学院在造血干细胞流程方面的专业知识，以及 Caring Cross 在增加患者获取机会方面的专业知识。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/advancing-the-manufacture-of-patient-accessible-cell-and-gene-therapies-at-place-of-care.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 11:46:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/advancing-the-manufacture-of-patient-accessible-cell-and-gene-therapies-at-place-of-care</guid></item><item><title>阿耳忒弥斯二号实时更新：宇航员进入高地球轨道，美国宇航局表示他们“精神抖擞”</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/artemis-ii-live-updates-crew-enters-high-earth-orbit-nasa-says-they-are-in-great-spirits</link><description>阿耳忒弥斯二号将创造历史，50多年来首次带领宇航员绕月飞行。四名宇航员将从位于佛罗里达州梅里特岛的 NASA 肯尼迪航天中心发射升空，开始为期 10 天的旅程。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/artemis-ii-live-updates-crew-enters-high-earth-orbit-nasa-says-they-are-in-great-spirits.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 11:31:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/artemis-ii-live-updates-crew-enters-high-earth-orbit-nasa-says-they-are-in-great-spirits</guid></item><item><title>升空！阿耳忒弥斯二号任务将人类送上月球——开启探索新时代</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/lift-off-artemis-ii-mission-sends-humans-to-the-moon-opening-a-new-era-of-exploration</link><description>希望、灵感和奇迹。让科幻变成现实。我向所有为这一重要使命做出贡献的勇敢而杰出的人们致敬。 3 关于 Artemis II 发射的文章。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/lift-off-artemis-ii-mission-sends-humans-to-the-moon-opening-a-new-era-of-exploration.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 11:16:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/lift-off-artemis-ii-mission-sends-humans-to-the-moon-opening-a-new-era-of-exploration</guid></item><item><title>经鼻递送的治疗性 DNA 疫苗融合了两个基因，有助于对抗结核病</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/therapeutic-nasally-delivered-dna-vaccine-fuses-two-genes-to-help-fight-tuberculosis</link><description>在一篇论文中&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/therapeutic-nasally-delivered-dna-vaccine-fuses-two-genes-to-help-fight-tuberculosis.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 11:01:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/therapeutic-nasally-delivered-dna-vaccine-fuses-two-genes-to-help-fight-tuberculosis</guid></item><item><title>引力波表明恒星起源黑洞存在“禁区”</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/gravitational-waves-suggest-a-forbidden-zone-for-stellar-origin-black-holes</link><description>由莫纳什大学领导的一个国际团队发现了一种罕见形式的恒星爆炸的证据，有助于揭示宇宙中最具灾难性的事件之一。在生命的尽头，大多数大质量恒星都会坍缩成黑洞——引力如此之大，甚至连光都无法逃脱的物体。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/gravitational-waves-suggest-a-forbidden-zone-for-stellar-origin-black-holes2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 10:46:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/gravitational-waves-suggest-a-forbidden-zone-for-stellar-origin-black-holes</guid></item><item><title>虚伪的神经科学指出大脑中的沟通障碍</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/the-neuroscience-of-hypocrisy-points-to-a-communication-breakdown-in-the-brain</link><description>一半的参与者接受了针对腹内侧前额叶皮层的实际刺激。另一半接受了假版本的治疗，称为假刺激。程序结束后，所有参与者完成相同的纸牌游戏和判断练习。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-neuroscience-of-hypocrisy-points-to-a-communication-breakdown-in-the-brain.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 10:31:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/the-neuroscience-of-hypocrisy-points-to-a-communication-breakdown-in-the-brain</guid></item></channel></rss>